{"tid":404790,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"比較下三國分別點起家，就知邊個英雄邊個狗雄","createTime":"2017-09-18T11:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T07:36:45.000Z","uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e6a529242ee79ee0163ce7f456791e170508802","tid":404790,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T11:17:35.000Z","msg":"用強勁既政治軍事外交能力，將敵人逐個ko<br />\n奉天子以令不臣<br />\n四面受敵之下亦能以至弱當至強<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小小年紀就成功自立，數年之間席捲江東六郡，死時僅廿六歲。其細佬廿歲未夠就接掌大事兼平定內亂，任賢能，再成功同義兄擋住強敵南下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地送地比佢，佢屢戰屢敗輸到仆街，之後好彩搵到個絕世治國大臣，之後等同族病死，幾廿歲人先起家。之後攻打人啦，打幾場廢仗都打九世，死q埋個軍師，仲要賴皮唔還地，最後發老皮，仲要比人火燒連營打敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70df2b5ac5b5ea34333bd8b0782bf4cc3cbfff6a","tid":404790,"uid":22449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T11:20:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4a8b0bf8881d8854634f652e182d9b02f6e992","tid":404790,"uid":2317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:05:02.000Z","msg":"曹操數值最高"},{"pid":"b36da45f0585f6b488c2c328266f085f90263e8e","tid":404790,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:40:48.000Z","msg":"曹操文武全材仲要係當世雙料冠軍<br />\n<br />\n根本冇得比"},{"pid":"4f15e6b2ec133df6bf1599ec13a6e793a8c771f6","tid":404790,"uid":36430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:47:10.000Z","msg":"曹操有家底，多親族<br />\n<br />\n孫策都有老豆遺臣，同玉璽借幾千兵<br />\n<br />\n劉備咩都冇，真係靠自己，絕對唔係廢"},{"pid":"2612a1fb1f64de277cd06167dc451fdfe3df02cc","tid":404790,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T01:39:10.000Z","msg":"大耳賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e9cd94cb62de817989228a5c0390df45c9653e","tid":404790,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:32:39.000Z","msg":"孟德文武雙全 帝王心術之高令人拍案<br />\n伯符係猂將 治國既話佢細佬前期屌打佢 後期都變到好似第二個人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但江東士族矛盾之大 啲兵仲要係部曲黎 佢都unite到啲人 係勁既<br />\n大耳好似高祖咁 得到一班能人異士相助 由無立錐之地去到進駐天府之國 得漢中 霸荊州 成一王業 都係真英雄"},{"pid":"7a8794008fa6062a9732ca28377d10e4076047bc","tid":404790,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:36:00.000Z","msg":"其實劉備好勁，輸咁多次都冇放棄，仲引到咁多人幫佢"},{"pid":"83cd39a9e3ed92ec38306ced3a3b24327205b508","tid":404790,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:36:26.000Z","msg":"大耳賊由小販撈起<br />\n另外兩件一個爺幹一個父兄幹<br />\n<br />\n根本三個都勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4fe5cf899fffc099d77e6341a32547243ec133","tid":404790,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:36:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實劉備好勁，輸咁多次都冇放棄，仲引到咁多人幫佢</blockquote><br />\n星期二出文"},{"pid":"c380e83b5142c1b6c23db7ba88427600aa6b620b","tid":404790,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:37:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實劉備好勁，輸咁多次都冇放棄，仲引到咁多人幫佢</blockquote><br />\n星期二出文</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"721a12e4ad9f94d591d6be0dcbfdbe69b964fc83","tid":404790,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:36:45.000Z","msg":"推返上黎睇下有冇大耳賊fans<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}